opennlp.ccg.hylo.graph
Class DefaultLFEdgeFactory

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.hylo.graph.DefaultLFEdgeFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
LFEdgeFactory, EdgeFactory<LFVertex,LFEdge>
public class DefaultLFEdgeFactory
extends Object
implements LFEdgeFactory

A factory for LF edges that creates edges from specified source and target vertices and an edge label. This class provides a default implementation of the LFEdgeFactory interface for instantiating LFGraphs.

Author:
Scott Martin
